<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8 not-prose">Word of the Day · 2-letter words</p>

<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 5 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">The -ENCE suffix creates abstract nouns from verbs and adjectives — evidence, patience, sequence. At 5 base points with the C tile worth 3, -ENCE words tend to reach 7-10 letters naturally, putting them squarely in bingo territory for the 50-point bonus.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Why -ENCE Matters in Scrabble</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
