    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">5–10</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Letter length range</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<p>The C tile in -ENCE is worth 3 points and appears twice in the bag. Most -ENCE words are 7+ letters, making them natural bingo plays.</p>

<p>The suffix is particularly valuable because it transforms common verbs into high-scoring nouns: REFER → REFERENCE, DIFFER → DIFFERENCE, SEQUENT → SEQUENCE.</p>

